					<h4 class="b3 t6"><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics" >Politics</a></h4>
		
	    						<ul>
						<li>
																		<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/andrewlansley"  rel="tag">Andrew Lansley</a> 															</li>
				</ul>
										
